Acting in accordance with the ordinary legislative procedure,

            

               
Whereas:

            

               
(1)
The 
COVID-19 pandemic is severely affecting people, companies, health systems and the econom
ies
 of Member States.
 
T
he Commission
,
 
in its 
Communication to the European Parliament, the European Council, the Council, the European economic and social committee and the 
C
ommittee of the regions 
of 27 
