ose reports 
should 
be 
temporarily 
suspended.

            

               
(9)
In order
 to 
facilitate the communication between investment firms and their clients and thus
 the investment process itself,
 
investment 
information should no longer be 
provided on paper
 
but should
, as a default option,
 be provided 
